title: Daewoo Extension Reel, 2 Way Socket with 5 Metre Cable, Heavy Duty with Resettable Safety Cut Out, Cassette Reel, Black and Blue
features: SAFETY CUTOUT – Equipped with a reset button, this extension reel will automatically shut off if it becomes too hot during use, ensuring absolute safety
2 WAY SOCKET – Compatible with UK plugs, allowing you to connect up to four devices for versatile use in your home, office, or garden
5 METRE CABLE – Offering a longer reach from your mains socket when you need the extra length both inside and outside. Avoid using outside in wet conditions
WINDING HANDLE – Use the winding handle to neatly store the cable when not in use, preventing tripping hazards
COMPACT DESIGN – Features a portable, lightweight design, making it easy to move around the house or office. Its slim and compact design also facilitates convenient storage when not in use
description: The Daewoo extension reel range offers versatile solutions for anyone in need of convenient power access. Perfect for homeowners, office workers, and garden enthusiasts alike, this range caters to various needs with its practical features. Whether you're setting up outdoor lighting for a garden party, powering multiple devices in your home office, or simply need to extend your reach to that distant socket, the Daewoo extension reel has you covered. Available in both 2-way and 4-way socket options and offering a variety of cable lengths for indoor and outdoor use (do not use in wet conditions outside), you can easily find the perfect fit for your requirements. Featuring a safety cutout function for peace of mind, a winding knob for tidy storage, and a compact design for easy portability, these extension reels are essential tools for any household or workspace. Say goodbye to tangled cords and limited power access with the Daewoo extension reel range.
